snippet.title: Widow's Walkabout Teaser Trailer - Walkabout Mini Golf
snippet.description:
This Thursday... putt your way through the mesmerizing mechanics,  phantasmal objects, Victorian architecture, and mischievous onlookers in Widow's Walkabout for a house of unending curiosities and supernatural shots.

Walkabout Mini Golf: Widow's Walkabout releases this Thursday, October 19th on Meta Quest, SteamVR, Pico, and PSVR2!
